<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Note Shared - {{appName}}</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #74b9ff 0%, #0984e3 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0; }
        .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background: #74b9ff; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .note-info { background: white; border-left: 4px solid #74b9ff; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 14px; }
        .emoji { font-size: 24px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1><span class="emoji">📝</span> Note Shared!</h1>
        <p>Kisi ne aapke saath note share kiya hai</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{recipientName}}! 👋</h2>
        
        <p><strong>{{sharedByName}}</strong> ne aapke saath ek note share kiya hai!</p>
        
        <div class="note-info">
            <h3>📄 Note Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>Title:</strong> {{noteTitle}}</p>
            <p><strong>Shared by:</strong> {{sharedByName}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>Note dekhne ke liye neeche button pe click karein:</p>
        
        <a href="{{noteUrl}}" class="button">View Note 👀</a>
        
        <p>{{appName}} mein aap:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>📖 Note read kar sakte hain</li>
            <li>💬 Comments add kar sakte hain</li>
            <li>🔄 Version history dekh sakte hain</li>
            <li>📤 Dusre users ke saath share kar sakte hain</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>{{appName}} access karne ke liye:</p>
        <a href="{{appUrl}}" style="color: #74b9ff;">{{appUrl}}</a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>{{appName}} Sharing Team 🤝</p>
        <p>Happy collaborating! 🎉</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>